docs.lead_paragraph: IN reflecting upon the different types of modern women one is struck by the fact how completely the morbid, reserved woman is out of date and how remorselessly the drooping, despondent type has been pushed to the wall.

headline.main: You Can Brighten Your Own Life and Help Others by a Course of Mental Suggestion.
